&lt;h1 id="make-abundance-for-the-world"&gt;Make Abundance for the World&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mar 3 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wealth isn&amp;rsquo;t about taking something from somebody else&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;
I think there is this notion that making money is evil, right? It&amp;rsquo;s rooted all the way back down to &amp;ldquo;money is the root of all evil.&amp;rdquo; People think that the bankers steal our money. It&amp;rsquo;s somewhat true in that, in a lot of the world, there&amp;rsquo;s a lot of theft going on all the time.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>